	<h1 class="title">这个布鲁克林的日本艺术家，谈了谈如何制作蓝染</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/121376/small/121376.jpg?1434268095" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Nara Shin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-27 08:31:35 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19745/medium/19745.jpg?1451026535" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


